There are several plotlines running through this great Italian gorefest.  Nobody can deliver in this genre like the Italians, and this doesn't disappoint.  It's twisted, shocking, never boring, and hard to watch at times because of its disturbing nature--exactly what I love & exactly what is surprisingly hard to find.  This is a true gem.
Gory!  ...but compelling.  It was disturbing, sure, but it wasn't so disturbing that it overshadowed the plot. Gore & plot worked together instead of distracted from one another.  A wonderful rarity.
I chose this rating cause the package came in the time frame that was given to me.  The package was brand new and for a good price.  I would shop with this company again.
It was okay, but don't waste your money.  From the beginning, it's evident this is a low-budget movie.  It has a good message, but it was also very predictable.
